\id HEB - Hona Bible 
\h Ibraniyaya 
\toc3 Ibraniyaya 
\toc2 Ibraniyaya 
\toc1 Ibraniyaya 
\mt1 Ibraniyaya 
\c 1  
\s1 Kalgha Faara sǝ tǝ mii Wanggǝn 
\p  
\v 1 Kaar, kalang Faara chichiyinǝm sǝ ahu kwamangya hangga tǝ ƙǝm hu sayi hangga tǝ mii annabiya.  
\v 2 Amma ahu ɓengginiya na yi mii ngwala ƙǝshiirha, kalang ɗǝ ƙǝm sǝ tǝ mii Wanggǝn. Tǝ Wan ɗa ni ǝnana Faara ǝngya heu, tǝƙǝm wur ɗa ndǝn a thlǝ ǝngya nǝn heu.  
\v 3 Ndǝghǝn ni kukwaryid mamnggid Faara tǝ ƙǝm ndǝghǝn ni thlǝgha Faara fa. Ndǝghǝn ni ƙǝsgha ǝngya heu ahu laɓarghǝn na tǝ sǝsǝmnda. A kwasamadɗi tsaɓang nǝn ƙǝm ɗǝ hu ɗimiyid nǝm, tsauka a talara a yisǝmad Faara na tǝ sǝsǝmnda fa kaan. 
\s1 Kal Wanɗi fathlǝngya Faara 
\p  
\v 4 Nanǝn kee wal mamnggirha nǝn kalgha fathlǝngya Faara ƙǝla ɗǝfang na nda thlǝma kalgha yi ndan mamnggirha. 
\q1  
\v 5 Ƙǝsǝr mbǝ tǝthlǝnda Faara sǝ ˈwana Faara ndang nda, 
\q1 “Waana ni sa, 
\q2 Tsauɗi Tsu a weeriya.” 
\m Nduwa ƙǝm, 
\q1 “Niya tsaurha Chin, 
\q2 Ndǝghǝnggi ƙǝm tsauka Waana wa.”\x * \xo 1:5 \xt Dzabura2:7; 2 Samaila7:14; 1 Ɗeleewar fa sǝngya17:13\x* 
\b  
\m  
\v 6 Amma ˈwanǝn thlǝn Wan ˈwadghǝn hu ƙǝshiirha ɗǝ, ndǝghǝn, 
\q1 “Ngwa fǝrangga fathlǝngya Faara mamnggirha.”\x * \xo 1:6 \xt Ɗeleewar nggǝr ngwa kumarha32:43\x* 
\m  
\v 7 Aten fathlǝngya Faara, ndaaghǝn, 
\q1 “Na Faara tsang fathlǝnggighǝn ƙǝla sǝsǝna, 
\q2 mafayighǝn ƙǝm tsawa nda ƙǝla sheneu waarha.”\x * \xo 1:7 \xt Dzabura104:4\x* 
\m  
\v 8 Amma aten Wanɗi ndǝghǝn, 
\q1 “Tsǝnggam kutǝryid wa, Faara, 
\q2 nǝn a tsaurha pakwanni ɗǝ, 
\q2 Sǝsal kutǝryid wa yi nggayirha ni 
\q1  
\v 9 Tar nggayirha ndǝna midwa, 
\q2 Kar na tar mbǝlfeerha! 
\q1 Tsaunǝn kee, yiwa Faara ndǝn ɗǝfowa aten shayiwa, 
\q2 ƙǝmo fǝɗeerha nǝn fa yi mbǝna farha.”\x * \xo 1:9 \xt Dzabura45:7-8\x*\x * \xo 1:9 \xt Dzabura45:6,7\x* 
\m  
\v 10 Ndǝghǝn ƙǝm, 
\q1 “Ka a katǝradghǝn, Chinǝm, 
\q2 Sa ǝnagha ƙǝshiirha, 
\q2 Talara ƙǝm tar harwa ni. 
\q1  
\v 11 Na nda a ngwalarha, 
\q2 Amma sa na a naarha sǝ; 
\q2 kanda heu na nda a tǝla ɗǝ ƙǝla kaɓarha na kaɓaarha ǝnaarha. 
\q1  
\v 12 Na a faɗang kanda ƙǝla ɓar kaɓarha, 
\q2 Na nda a nggǝrang kanda hai ƙǝla na niifa mbeɗeng karidghǝn hai. 
\q1 Amma sa mba tam kyaharra hai wa, 
\q2 Mbǝ hurad wa tam ngwalarha wa.”\x * \xo 1:12 \xt Dzabura102:25-27\x* 
\m  
\v 13 Ahur fathlǝngya Faara mbusǝ ˈwana Faara ndang nda, 
\q1 “Tsawu a yisǝmanna 
\q2 ƙǝl tsawang ni fatsanggiwa 
\q2 akamu saryiwa.”\x * \xo 1:13 \xt Dzabura110:1\x* 
\p  
\v 14 Fathlǝngya heu sǝsǝn fatarya ni kee. Thlǝnna Faara kanda ka a ɗangganda fingyayina sǝ na har langaad hǝrǝkrha. 
\c 2  
\s1 Yiyi thlǝmaarha aten kyathla hai 
\p  
\v 1 Tsaunǝn kee, taama kwarǝm aten ǝngya sǝk nǝm, a kwar wum wa nǝm a kyathla hai ma kwamana.  
\v 2 Tsaunǝn laɓarɗi thlǝk na fathlǝngya Faara ƙǝkafek ni, fingya kargha takkwaghǝn, nduwa kar ɗa fa a ǝna taara nda tǝghǝn wal nda yindan tsǝtsǝlla kamngga a kanda.\f + \fr 2:2 \ft Ibraniyaya 1:1; Nggurub ngwa kumarha 33.2; Tar fathlǝngya 7:53; Ibraniyaya 10:28\f* 
\v 3 Ƙǝƙǝn nǝm wal hǝrǝkrha a kar wum tǝ mamnggid hǝrǝkrha wa? Ƙǝsǝr Chinǝm tafadghǝn, ndǝn katǝrangga pǝrrǝghǝn hai, fingya sǝkka ndǝn kanda pǝrangga ndaarha ƙǝm ƙǝkafek ni.  
\v 4 A mbǝɗiya chikka Faara yighǝn shedawa aten yindan tǝ ǝnsakhkya, tǝ ǝnwultengya tǝ ǝngya mǝmanggǝn ɗǝɗamǝn-ɗǝɗamǝn, tǝ fǝrra Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda ɗǝɗamǝn-ɗǝɗamǝn, ndǝghang nǝn ɗǝ ƙǝla tǝrna midghǝn. 
\s1 Tsau Yeeso Niifa 
\p  
\v 5 Malangwa Faara ndǝn fathlǝnggighǝn ǝna kutǝryirha nda aten Ƙǝshidɗi na ɓayi nǝm a ndikrha atenggǝn nanǝnya wa.  
\v 6 Amma na mbǝrha sǝ hu ɗeleewar Faara ndagha: 
\q1 “Mani nafiya tǝ waasa in na ɓillarha tǝ kanda, 
\q1 Nduwa wan niifa na lafrha?  
\v 7 Tsang na kanda ngguchit ma fathlǝngya Faara, 
\q1 Faɗang na kanda tǝ yi mamnggirha tǝ hǝhasyirha,  
\v 8 fǝrang sǝsǝmnda kanda aten ǝngya heu.” 
\m Malang ɗǝ ǝngya heu a kamu ndan, mbǝ ˈya sǝ ɗǝfang na Faara man patu ɗǝ ma kanda wa. Ko mbuwa nǝm nanǝnya a naa ǝngya heu na a kamu ndan wa.\f + \fr 2:8 \fq Dzabura 8:4-6; 1Korontiyaya 15:25\f* 
\v 9 Amma ƙǝm naɗǝm Yeeso, tsauka ahu sayi ngguchit a kamu fathlǝngya Faara, nanǝnya faɗang nda nǝghǝn tǝ mamnggirha tǝ hǝhasyirha hu sǝsadghǝn yi mǝrra. Nanǝn kee, ka nggayid Faara ni, ƙǝsna Yeeso mǝrra fa ka kowunni.\f + \fr 2:9 \ft Tar Fathlǝngya Yeeso 2:33; 3:13; Filibiyaya 2:9; Filibiyaya 2:7-9; Yahaya 3:16; 2 Korontiyaya 5:15\f* 
\v 10 Ƙǝsǝr mǝmǝl ni ǝnanǝn ǝngya heu tǝƙǝm nana ǝngya sǝ heu, ahu ɓang nda wundakhnaya ɓa hangga ahu mamnggirha ɓa. Nanǝn kee, mǝmǝl ni tsang nǝn tǝ inang nda kwaman hǝrǝkrǝ ndan hai chahal hu sǝsaarha.\f + \fr 2:10 \ft Romaya 11:36; Luka 24:26; Ibraniyaya 7:28\f* 
\v 11 Ƙǝsǝr ndǝghǝn na a tsang niifa chahal tǝ fingya ˈwa nanda tsang kanda chahal, na nda hu minda tal. Nanǝn kee mbǝ shilee ƙǝsang Yeeso a aahɗǝ kanda shayighǝn wa,  
\v 12 ndǝghǝn, 
\q1 “Niya pǝr thlǝm wa a shayina. 
\q1 Niya fal thlǝm wa a pathlang fiya a wum nda hai ka a tǝrang shilee nda Faara in.” \f + \fr 2:12 \ft Dzabura 22:22 \f* 
\v 13 Nggǝrghǝn ndaarha, 
\q1 “Niya mbǝrsaarha tǝghǝn.” 
\m Tǝ ƙǝm, 
\q1 “Kulo nggi ya tǝ wanggini fǝree na Faara.”\f + \fr 2:13 \ft Ishaya 8:17; Ishaya 8:18; Yahaya 10:29 \f* 
\p  
\v 14 Tsau nǝn wanggini na nda tǝ thlu farha fa tǝ fara, ndǝghǝnggi ƙǝm tsauɗǝ kee. Əna nǝn kee ƙǝsǝr hu mǝrrǝghǝn, ɓǝlang ɗǝ sǝsǝmnda tǝ ƙǝs mǝra ha, ndǝna Sheetan, \f + \fr 2:14 \ft Yahaya 1:14; 1 Korontiyaya 15:54-57; 2 Timoti 1:10; 1 Yahaya 3:8 \f* 
\v 15 kwasanggǝn fingya hai hu tsawud ndan na a ǝna tar mafayirha ƙǝsǝr ka tǝrǝm mǝrra.\f + \fr 2:15 \ft 2 Timoti 1:7 \f* 
\v 16 Ƙǝsǝr ƙǝkafek mbǝ fathlǝngya Faara nǝn a ɗang kanda sǝ wa, amma chichiiya Ibrahim.  
\v 17 Tsaunǝn kee, ngwa tsauka ƙǝla kanda, ko ƙǝƙǝn ni tsauka tǝ haɗang nda fiya fa tǝ firis na manggǝn tǝ ƙǝkafek fa hu tar Faara. Tǝnǝn fǝr sataka yi chahang ɗimiyid ndan fiya ɗǝ. \f + \fr 2:17 \ft Filibiyaya 2:7; Ibraniyaya 5:2; Ibraniyaya 4:14,15; 7:26,28; Ibraniyaya 5:1\f* 
\v 18 Ƙǝsǝr ndǝghǝn tafadghǝn tǝk ɗǝ sǝsaarha fa a sayidɗi ƙǝƙǝrang na nda, tsǝk ɗǝ ƙǝm na a ɗanggǝn fingya sǝ a nanda a ƙǝƙǝrang kanda.\f + \fr 2:18 \ft Ibraniyaya 4:15\f* 
\c 3  
\s1 Kal Yeeso Musa mu 
\p  
\v 1 Tsaunǝn kee shayina fatakkwaya na chahal, kun pet na fad nun walgha adɗi na a talara, sheeman teena Yeeso fa, nǝm aarha tǝthlǝnda Faara tǝ ƙǝm firis na manggǝn sheeda nǝm. \f + \fr 3:1 \ft Ibraniyaya 2:11; Ibraniyaya 2:17; Ibraniyaya 4:14\f* 
\v 2 Ənaɗǝ taara tǝ ƙǝkafekkirha a niifɗi thlǝngga ndǝn ɓa, ƙǝla ǝnana Musa ƙǝkafekkirha ahu targhǝn ahur nafiya Faara.\f + \fr 3:2 \ft Ɗeleewar thlǝtta 12:7 \f* 
\v 3 Heu tǝ kee, wal Yeeso fǝrra mamnggirha kaan ma Musa, ƙǝla niifa tǝngga ƙǝnna kalɗǝ ƙǝnɗi mamnggirha.  
\v 4 Ƙǝsǝr kala wure na niifasǝ tǝngga ndǝn, amma tǝ tǝn ǝngya heu Faara ni.  
\v 5 Nana Musa tǝ ƙǝkafek fa ahu ǝngya heu a mbed nafiya Faara, fǝrɗǝ shedawa tǝ ǝngya ɓana Faara thlǝkrha a mbee.\f + \fr 3:5 \ft Kyarhaɓa 14:31; Ɗeleewar thlǝtta 12:7\f* 
\v 6 Amma Ƙǝrǝsti nǝghǝn tǝ ƙǝkafek fa tsaunǝn ndǝghǝn ni Wee na aten nafiya Faara heu. Ƙǝm ni wurighǝn, a ɗǝɗǝm mbeeɗǝ tǝ shembe tǝ shiiten ɗi nǝm a taala sǝ. 
\s1 Ƙǝs thlǝmaarha aten yamid fǝrƙǝkafek 
\p  
\v 7 Nanǝn kee, ƙǝla ndana Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda, 
\q1 “A weeriya a sǝk ɗun kwad uradghǝn, 
\q2  
\v 8 a na hur nun kakrak wa, 
\q1 ƙǝla ǝna nun kakyathlanga, 
\q2 a sayid ƙǝƙǝrra na a kaheerha wa. 
\q1  
\v 9 A mbǝɗi ƙǝƙǝree na chichiyi nun sǝ, 
\q2 ko nanǝn nanda taara ǝnani yi huraya kumnggit faɗa. 
\q1  
\v 10 Ndǝghǝn ɗani sǝbna hurna ɗǝ tǝ nafiya ƙǝshiid farɗi ndǝn ndaani, 
\q2 ‘Na ahur ndan inggun ma nggi, 
\q2 kar ǝna ˈya ndang ni kanda.’ 
\q1  
\v 11 Hǝrǝmna hurna sǝbrha ɗǝ aah Faara ni ndee, 
\q2 ‘Mba nda tam kyarha hu yiɓǝdna hai wa.’ ”\f + \fr 3:11 \ft Ibr 4.3,5; Dzabura 95.7-11 \f* 
\m  
\v 12 Shayina, kwarama, naɗǝ hur nun naarha tǝ mbǝlfeerha, tǝ yamid fǝrƙǝkafek, na a kyakhrun hai malanggun Faara na tǝ yibrha wa.  
\v 13 Amma nama narha fǝrang kaali ndan kala ɗathla mbǝrha fa hai. Ənama taara tǝ fara nǝm aarha, “Weeriya,” amana niifa narha tal ahur hukrha ɗimiyirha ndǝn nagha hurghǝn kakrak.\f + \fr 3:13 \ft Ibraniyaya 10:24,25; Afisaya 4:22\f* 
\v 14 Nǝm a wumteena tǝ Ƙǝrǝsti a ish ɗǝm tǝ shembe ƙǝla ˈwa nǝm fǝrƙǝkafek ta mii ngwaladghǝn ɗǝ. \f + \fr 3:14 \ft Mbǝdghǝn 6\f* 
\v 15 Ƙǝla ndaana nda, 
\q1 “A weeriya a sǝkɗun uradghǝn, 
\q1 A tsang ɗun hur nun kakrak ƙǝla a sayid kakyathlang ɗi wa.”\f + \fr 3:15 \ft 7:8; Dzabura 95:7,8\f* 
\v 16 Nda wunni sǝkka uradghǝn, nggǝra nda ǝna kakyathlaanga tǝghǝn? Mbǝ nafina ni kyang na Musa kanda sǝ a chehweed Masar wa?\f + \fr 3:16 \ft Ɗeleewar Thlǝtta 14.29; Dzabura 106.26\f* 
\v 17 Nda wunni sǝbna hur Faara ɗǝ tǝ kanda yi hurarha kumnggit faɗa? Mbǝ nafina ni ǝnagha ɗimiyirha, mǝrna nda a kaheerha wa?  
\v 18 Nda wunni aah na Faara thlǝmnggǝn aten ndan tǝ ndaarha mba tam wal yibrha a mishim ndǝghǝn wa? Mbǝ nafina ni kargha miighǝn fa wa?\f + \fr 3:18 \ft Ɗeleewar thlǝtta 14:20-23; Ibraniyaya 4:6\f* 
\v 19 Ƙǝla nǝm hai kee ashe ka yamid fǝrƙǝkafekkid ndan ni walwa nanda yibrha a mishim ndǝghǝn.\f + \fr 3:19 \ft Yahaya 3:36\f* 
\c 4  
\s1 Far yiɓǝd nafiya Faara 
\p  
\v 1 Tsaunǝn kee, hǝrǝmna ɗǝf miighǝn yi kyarha hu yibrha hai ɓalghǝn sǝ, tama kwarǝm kaan, amana tal ahur nun ƙǝɗeng kyarha sahai.  
\v 2 Ƙǝsǝr sǝk ɗǝm Laɓarɗi na Mbǝnggǝn ƙǝla kanda ƙǝm, amma laɓarɗi ɗang ngwa kanda sǝ wa, thlǝwa ndan fa tǝ ƙǝkafekkirha wa.  
\v 3 Amma ƙǝm fǝrgha ƙǝkafek, ƙǝm ni na a kyarha hu yiɓǝdɗa hai. Ɗalama teena hai tǝ laɓar Faara ndanǝn, “Sǝb hurna ɗǝ aah ni thlǝmna tǝ ndaarha, ‘Mba nda tam kyarha hu yibrha hai wa.’ ” Ndaana Faara kee ko nanǝn ˈwaɗǝ teena ngwalang ɗǝ targhǝn ka a sayidɗi ǝnanǝn ƙǝshiirha.  
\v 4 Ƙǝsǝr ahu ma mbǝrha thlǝk ɗǝ laɓar ɓeena yi mǝd tǝ ndaarha, “Afar ɓeena yi mǝd yib Faara ahu targhǝn ǝnanǝn heu.”  
\v 5 Tǝ kǝm nggǝr nda thlǝkƙǝn tǝ ndaarha, “Mba nda tam kyarha hu mbǝd yiɓǝd na hai wa.”  
\v 6 Kaar pǝr nda laɓarɗi ya na mbǝnggǝn aten yiɓǝdɗi, amma fingya pǝrang na nda Laɓar Faara kanda kyawa nda sahai wa ƙǝsǝr fǝrwanda ƙǝkafek tǝghǝn wa.  
\v 7 Tǝrgha nggǝrghǝn ɗǝf fara, aaghǝnǝn, “Weeriya”. Thlǝkƙǝn farɗiya akwasamad huraya hangga a mii Ndauda, ƙǝla ndaana laɓar Faara na chichireethlee hai kaar, “A weeriya a sǝk ɗun urad Faara, a tsang ɗun hur nun kakrak wa.”  
\v 8 A ndam fǝrang Djeshiwa yibrha kanda, kam nggǝr wa Faara sakh fara sǝmǝn yi far yibrha wa.  
\v 9 Ta weeri ɗaɓa ya Ɓalgha far yiɓǝdɗa sǝ ya yi nafiya Faara.  
\v 10 Ƙǝsǝr kala nafiya kyagha hu yiɓǝdɗa hai ki Faara ya, yib nda hu tar ndan ƙǝla yibna Faara ahu yighǝn taara.  
\v 11 Tsaunǝn kee, taama djitǝm na a kyam hu yiɓǝdɗa hai ya, amawana niifa kyarha hu yamid kar mii Faara fa ƙǝla ǝnana nafiya Isǝreelaya.  
\v 12 Ƙǝkafek, na laɓar Faara nǝghǝn tǝ yibrha fa, tǝ shembed taara ƙǝm. Chimndghǝn kalɗǝ yi thlaukh ƙǝlara na tǝ mee sǝri. Nǝn kyathla ta ahur niifa ɗǝ, ndǝghanggǝn sǝsǝna hai tǝ yibrha, tǝ ƙǝm ta hu shileerha ɗǝ. Nǝn sǝnang numad ˈya hai na mid niifa tǝ numadghǝn.  
\v 13 Mbǝ ˈyasǝ ǝnana nda hu ƙǝshiirha na ɓǝɓee a yid Faara wa. Əngya heu nǝghǝn a pǝpal hu yidghǝn ndǝghǝn nǝm a fǝrang kirǝssa ǝngya ǝna nǝm. 
\s1 Yeeso ndǝna mamnda Firistaya 
\p  
\v 14 Tsaunǝn nǝghǝm tǝ mamnda Firis ha, Yeeso Wan Faara ɗǝgha talara ɗǝ ta mbed Faara ɗǝ, taama ishim aten fǝrƙǝkafekkid nǝm ƙǝla ndaa nǝm.  
\v 15 Ƙǝsǝr mamnda Firis ɗi kyanǝm ya mbǝ yanɗa ni mbuwa nǝm haɗang fa ka ƙǝɗi nǝm wa. Amma nǝghǝm tǝ mamnda Firis ƙǝƙǝrang na nda hu kwamangya hangga ƙǝla nanǝm, amma ndǝghǝn nggi mbǝ tǝ ɗimiyirha fa wa.  
\v 16 Tsaunǝn kee taama nam hwas-hwas ɗǝm ɗǝ tsau tǝ tsǝnggam kutǝryid Faara fa, tǝnǝm haɗang nda fa kaɗa nggayirha nǝm na a ɗang ƙǝm sǝ ana mid nǝm sǝ thlaara. 
\c 5  
\p  
\v 1 Kala manda Firis na nda wurghǝn sǝ ahur fiya ƙǝsǝr a ǝna tar Faara nǝn a meyed fiya, ndǝghǝn ni fǝr ǝn fǝra tǝ ǝna sataka yi chakh ɗimiyirha.  
\v 2 Tsaunǝn ndǝghǝnggi nǝghǝn tǝ yighǝn ƙǝɗiirha, nǝn mbang takkwarha tǝ fingya na tǝ yamid sǝnda tǝ sammayirha tǝ fingya na a kyathla hai.  
\v 3 Ndǝghǝn ɗa nǝn ǝna sataka yi altenggǝn yi chakh ɗimiyirha tǝ yi fiya ƙǝm.  
\v 4 Mbǝ niifa sǝ na wur fadghǝn tsauka mamnda firis ka nana midghǝn a fǝrang mamnggirha nda wa. Na niifa mbang tsaurha firis na manggǝn kee a aah Faara ndǝn ƙǝla aah nǝn Haruna.  
\v 5 Nǝghǝn kee ƙǝm, mbǝ Ƙǝrǝsti ni wurgha altenggǝn tsauka Firis na manggǝn wa. Faara ndǝn wurgha ndǝn, ndǝn ndangna Faara, “Waana ni sa. A weeriya tsauɗi Tsu.”  
\v 6 Nggǝrghǝn ndaarha a mbǝrha pak, “Firis ni sa pakwanɗǝ, ƙǝla saghang na Melkidzedek hai.”  
\v 7 A sayidɗi na Yeeso hu ƙǝshiirha, hwan ɗǝ Faara tǝ tǝrha kaan har tǝ aam yirha, a niifɗi na mbang hǝrghang nda ma mǝrra. Sǝk Faara hwandǝghǝn ƙǝsǝr nǝn ǝna taara tǝ ˈya ndang na Faara tǝ fǝrang mamnggirha.  
\v 8 Ko nanǝn Yeeso Wan Faara ni, tsaha ɗǝ ǝna taara hu ǝngya sanǝn fa.  
\v 9 A sayidɗi tsaunǝn lǝlǝgɗa, tsauka ndǝghǝn ni kwaman hǝrǝkrha yi pakwanɗǝ a fingya heu na a ǝna taara tǝ ˈya ndaanǝn,  
\v 10 ahu kiya ni faɗang na Faara tsauka Firis na manggǝn ƙǝla saghang na Melkidzedek hai. 
\s1 Yiyi thlǝmarha aten wutta samarha ɗǝ 
\p  
\v 11 Aten laɓar ɗiya na ǝngya sǝ hangga na minnan thlǝkrha, amma nǝghǝn pǝɗaghǝn na a pǝrang nggǝnan kun, ƙǝsǝr mbun mbang sǝnang ˈya hai wed wa.  
\v 12 Kam ɗǝ kun nanǝnya tsawun fa tsahaya ha, amma na mid nun sǝ a nggǝrgha niifa tsahanggǝn kun ha aten ǝngya kamngga hu laɓar Faara. Ƙǝl ɓi thlaarha kee ndǝn ɓalna mid nun, ma yaarha.  
\v 13 Kala niifa tsauna ɓi thlaarha ǝnnadghǝn mii, wufar wee ni, sǝngwa ǝna kwaman ˈya na ngga wa.  
\v 14 Amma ǝnnarhami na kakrak ndǝna yi fingya mangga, na a ǝna taara tǝ numad ndan ƙǝtsar, na a hwathlang ngganda ˈya hai na ngga tǝ tar mbǝlfeerha. 
\c 6  
\p  
\v 1 Tsaunǝn kee, taama malang nggǝm djib katǝra tsaharhaha ˈwa nǝm waala aten Ƙǝrǝsti, ɗǝm mbeeɗǝ, tǝ chik sǝnda. Kamngwa a nggǝrghǝm katǝrang tsaharhaha aten mal ɗimiyirha aten ǝngya na ɓang mǝra ɓa tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek a Faara wa,  
\v 2 tǝƙǝm sǝk laɓaara aten mbaptisma, tǝ fǝr parka, tǝ yi thliirha sǝ hu mǝrra, tǝ ngwa kumad ngwala ƙǝshiirha.  
\v 3 A nggǝm Faara fa, nǝm a ɗǝrha mbeeɗǝ.  
\v 4 Ƙǝsǝr nǝghǝn pǝɗaghǝn mbanggǝm wuɗang fingya thlǝgha laɓarɗa fa nggǝra nda samarha ɗǝ. Fingya ˈwa nanda ɓang kanda hu kukwaryid Faara ɓa, taarangga ǝngya fa na ngga a talara, wal nda yindan Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda,  
\v 5 tǝƙǝm taarangga mbǝnda laɓar Faara fa tǝ sǝsǝmnda ƙǝshiirha na ɓayi.  
\v 6 Amma fingya wudgha samarha ɗǝ hu fǝrƙǝkafekkid ndan mbǝ kwamana sǝ na a wuɗang nggǝm kanda ɓa na a mal ɗimiyid ndanda wa. Ƙǝsǝr na nda a nggǝr tawang Wan Faara ɗǝ aten kaɗiirha, fǝrang shilee nda a pǝpal. 
\p  
\v 7 Chehweerha na a sang aam ˈyaara na a ɓarha tenggǝn hai ƙǝtsar, na kyang hǝfya sǝ fǝr ǝnnarhami nǝn ka a thlar fingya yina nǝn na a huɗaghǝn, nǝn wal parkad Faara.  
\v 8 Amma ana chehweerha a kyang ndakhkya sǝ tǝ hwaliiya mbǝ ngga wa, na Faara a shiwang nda. A kwasamadghǝn nǝn a djirha ɗǝ.  
\v 9 Shayina, ko nanǝn thlǝk ɗan tur laɓarɗiya, sǝnɗansǝ nun a thlǝ parka na ngga yi hǝrǝkrha na fingya a waala.  
\v 10 Faara mbǝ tǝ yamid nggayirha fa wa. Taara ǝnang nun tǝ nggǝmnda kyaɗang nun hu thlaara a nafiyighǝn, ƙǝla nanun a ɗǝrha mbeeɗǝ tǝ ɗang kanda sǝ.  
\v 11 ˈYa na minnan ndǝna kowunni ahur nun na a djitigha kee ta mii ngwaladghǝn ɗǝ, tǝna ǝnggini nun a shiteena atenggǝn lǝghǝtta.  
\v 12 Mbǝ minnan sǝ a tsawun nafiya na tǝ sǝbrha yid wa, amma tsahama fingya yini hu fǝrƙǝkafek, tǝ ƙǝrǝsta har langaad ɗǝf mii ɗa nda. 
\s1 Ƙǝkafek ni ɗǝf mii Faara 
\p  
\v 13 A sayidɗi ɗǝfna Faara miighǝn a Ibrahim, ɗǝf ɗǝ miighǝn tǝ aah thlǝmnggǝn. Tsaunǝn mbǝ niifa sǝ kalgha ndǝn na a aah thlǝmnggǝn nǝn wa, ndǝn aah nǝn thlǝmnggǝn.  
\v 14 Ndagha Faara, “Ƙǝkafek, niya fǝro parka, niya tsawang chichiyiwa na nda hangga kaan.”  
\v 15 A kwasamadɗi ƙǝrǝs na Ibrahim kaan, tǝrgha fǝrangga Faara ǝnɗi ɗǝf nǝn miighǝn.  
\v 16 Na fiya aah Faara aten niifa kalgha kanda mamnggirha. Aah Faara ndǝna a kyad mii ngwala ngaala.  
\v 17 Nǝghǝn kee ƙǝm, ana mid Faara sǝ a kyad ndaarha nǝn ˈya ndanǝn ƙǝkafek ni a nafiya ɗǝfnǝn miighǝn nǝn aah thlǝmnggǝn ka a kyanggǝn ngaala ɗǝ ahur ndan a kyad ndaarha nǝn mbǝ tam kyakhrang miighǝn hai wa.  
\v 18 Na ǝngya sǝ sǝri mbuwa tam kyaharra hai, mbuwana Faara nggaɓarha atenggǝn. Nanǝn kee ƙǝm walgha mbǝd tsaurha nǝn a fǝrang kaali ƙǝm kaan na a ƙǝs ǝnɗa nǝm ha nǝm a shang teena fa na a mbed nǝm.  
\v 19 Shiiten ɗi kyanǝm ya ƙǝkafek ni nǝn ishang huten nǝm. Nǝn kyarha hura ɗǝ kaan, ta ƙǝsǝr shishamar ɗa ɗǝ na a mbǝrha chahal a talara.  
\v 20 Yeeso ndǝn ˈwagha kyarha mbǝɗa ɗǝ a meyed nǝm, tsaunǝn ndǝghǝn ni Firis na manggǝn yi pakwanɗǝ ƙǝla saghang na Melkidzedek hai. 
\c 7  
\s1 Tsaurha Firis tur yi Melkidzedek 
\p  
\v 1 Melkidzedek kutǝr Salem ni, tǝ ƙǝm Firis yi Faara na manggǝn kalgha mbǝrha mu. Ƙǝmaghǝn tǝ Ibrahim a sayidɗi nǝn a wutta ɓa a kwasamadɗi hǝb nǝn yanda ǝnanǝn tǝ kutǝrya kal nǝn kanda mu, ƙǝma na nda hai, ɗǝfang parka nǝn in.  
\v 2 Tǝrgha Ibrahim fǝrang ǝnfǝra nǝn tal hu kum yi ǝngya wal nǝn ɓa hu yanda. Thlǝm Melkidzedek ndaarha ni, “Kutǝra yi nggayirha.” Tǝƙǝm, “Kutǝr Salem ni,” ndaarha ni, “Kutǝr tsawud ɗǝɗemnggirha.”  
\v 3 Mbǝ chireethla sǝ kyadgha chin Melkidzedek tǝ man nduwa turyighǝn wa. Mbǝ katǝra ɓenggǝn sǝ nduwa mii ngwala tsawudghǝn wa. Amma firis ni ndǝghǝn yi pakwanɗǝ, nǝghǝn ƙǝla Wan Faara.  
\v 4 Ƙǝlaman tur mamnggid niifɗiya. Ko Ibrahim riigha mii na chichid nǝm fǝrang ɗǝ tal hu kum ǝngya har nǝn ɓa ka yanda.  
\v 5 Nanǝnya ɗeleewar ngyakhrha Musa kyadɗǝ ndaarha turya Lawiya tsauka firis na nda thlǝ ǝnfǝra tal hu kum a haar nafiya Isǝreela ko nanǝn turya Ibrahim ni.  
\v 6 Amma Melkidzedek mbuwa tur Lawiya, thlǝɗǝ ǝnfǝra a haar Ibrahim, ɗǝfang parka nǝn Ibrahim teena ndǝghǝnggi ˈwagha thlǝ ɗǝfmi Faara.  
\v 7 Mbǝ ngaala sǝ wa yi na fǝr parka kalɗǝ yanɗi na a thlǝ parka mamnggirha.  
\v 8 A mbǝɗiya, firistaya na hu turya Lawiya nafiya ni mǝrgha, na nda thlǝ ǝnfǝra tal hu kum a haar fiya. Amma aten Melkidzedek, thlǝgha ǝnfǝra a haar Ibrahim thlǝk ndan tǝ ndaarha nǝghǝn tǝ yibrha fa.  
\v 9 Nanǝn kee, nǝm ndaarha Lawi tafadghǝn, tsauka turyighǝn ni na thlǝ ǝnfǝra, fǝrɗǝ yighǝn ǝnfǝra haaɗǝ a haar Ibrahim,  
\v 10 ƙǝsǝr a sayidɗi ƙǝmana Ibrahim hai tǝ Melkidzedek nggǝt wanda Lawi ˈwan wa, amma nǝghǝn hu turya chichidghǝn. 
\s1 Na Yeeso ƙǝla Melkidzedek 
\p  
\v 11 Nanǝn kee, a ndam firistayirha yi Lawiya nǝghǝn mǝmǝl tǝ yi ɗeleewar ngyakhrha Musa fǝrang na nda Isǝreelaya, kama na firis nggǝr kyarha ɓa pak, na mǝmǝl tǝ tur yi Melkidzedek, mbǝ tur yi Haruna wa.  
\v 12 Ƙǝsǝr a nggǝrang nda kwaman firistayirha hai, tsauɗǝ tǝta ni a nggǝrang ngganda tsahad ngyakhrha hai ƙǝm.  
\v 13 Ƙǝsǝr firisɗi nǝm a thlǝk ǝnggini atenggǝn ya, nǝghǝn hu turya pak, mbǝ niifa sǝ ƙǝm ahur tur yini ˈwagha ǝna tar firis a mbǝd nji sataka wa.  
\v 14 Ƙǝsǝr nǝghǝn a pǝpal tǝ ndaarha Chinǝm ɓaghǝn ɓa ahu turya Yahuda, mbǝ ˈya sǝ ˈwana Musa thlǝkrha aten firistaya tǝ ndaarha na nda kyarha ɓa ahu turya Yahuda wa.  
\v 15 Laɓarɗi thlǝk nǝm ya tsauɗǝ ƙǝkafek, hǝrǝm nǝn naarha na firis sǝ na ƙǝla Melkidzedek kyagha ɓa.  
\v 16 Ndǝghǝnggi tsauka firis mbǝ ka ngyakhrha nduwa ǝntin thlufarha wa, amma nǝghǝn aten sǝsǝmnda yibrha mbuwana mii ngwaladghǝn sǝ.  
\v 17 Ƙǝsǝr pǝr ndan tǝ ndaarha, “Firis ni sa yi pakwanɗǝ, ƙǝla tur yi Melkidzedek.”  
\v 18 Malang nda tsahad kaar a man patu ɗǝ ƙǝsǝr ka yamid sǝsǝmndǝghǝn tǝ yamid thlarǝghǝn.  
\v 19 Ƙǝsǝr tsahad ɗeleewar Musa mbǝ tsawang ˈya lǝlǝgɗa wa. Amma nanǝnya na shiteena sǝ na ngga kaan ndusangga ƙǝm thlǝmad Faara ɓa.  
\v 20 Yanɗiya mbǝ kula tǝ aah thlǝm Faara wa. Fingya tsauka firisya, aah wa nda thlǝmnggǝn Faara wa.  
\v 21 Amma aahɗǝ thlǝm Faara kyanǝn hu tar firis hai ndangna Faara, “Chinǝm aah ɗǝ thlǝm Faara mbǝ tam hwasang ˈya ndanǝn wa, ‘Firis ni sa pakwanɗǝ.’”  
\v 22 Ƙǝsǝr ka aah Faarɗi ya, Yeeso ni katenggǝn na mbang tsawang nda ɗǝfmi ɗiya tsauka ngga tǝ Faara.  
\v 23 Firisya yi kaar na nda hangga, ƙǝsǝr mǝrra ndǝn ˈyaɗangga mana kanda fa a ɗǝnda mbeeɗǝ tǝ tar ndan.  
\v 24 Amma ƙǝsǝr na Yeeso tǝ yibrha fa pakwanɗǝ, Yighǝn firistayirha yi pakwanni ɗǝ.  
\v 25 Tsaunǝn kee, nǝn mbang hǝrghang nda nafiya ɓagha thlǝmad Faara ɓa tǝ man fadghǝn. Ƙǝsǝr nǝn naarha tsǝ laɓaara tǝ Faara a meyed ndan.  
\v 26 Tur mamnda firis ɗani ya na mid nǝm ƙǝsǝr nǝghǝn chahal, chahal kula ǝn ˈyaara fa, nǝghǝn inggun ma fa ɗimiya, tǝ mamnggirha a talakh talara.  
\v 27 Mbǝ ƙǝla fingya mamngya firistaya wa. Mbǝ midghǝnsǝ nagha a fǝr sataka ƙǝtsar wa. ˈWaghǝn fǝr sataka ka ɗimiyid aal fadghǝn, a nggǝrgha ǝnaarha ka ɗimiya fiya. Fǝrghǝn sataka katǝra tal ka ɗimiyid ndan a sayidɗi fǝr nǝn fadghǝn.  
\v 28 A hu ɗeleewar ngyakhrha Musa na nda wur mamnda firis hu ƙǝɗiirha nanǝnsǝ ahur fiya. Amma aah thlǝm Faara, ɓaghǝn ɓa a kwasamad ngyahadɗi, wurghǝn Wanɗi, tsauka chahal pakwanɗǝ. 
\c 8  
\s1 Yinǝm Mamnda Firis ndǝna Ƙǝrǝsti 
\p  
\v 1 ˈYa nǝm a ndaarha nanǝnya ndǝna, nǝghǝm tǝ Mamnda firis na tsau hu tsǝnggam kutǝryirha a yisǝmad Faara a talara,  
\v 2 tǝ ǝna taara a mbǝrha na chahal, ahu ka chamɗi na ngga ǝnana Chinǝm, mbǝ yanɗi ǝnana niifa wa.  
\v 3 Kala mamnda firis targhǝn ni fǝr ǝnfǝra tǝ sataka, nanǝn kee mamnda firis ɗi kyanǝm ya tǝtani a fǝr ˈya nǝn.  
\v 4 Andam nǝghǝn hu ƙǝshiirha ni, kam mbǝ tam tsaurha firis wa, ƙǝsǝr na firistaya sǝ na fǝr satakhkya ƙǝla sakhna ɗeleewar ngyakrha.  
\v 5 Na firistayini ya ǝna tar ndan a mbǝrha na chahal na ƙǝla ǝngya na a talara. Ƙǝsǝr a sayidɗi na Musa a taksa chama yi Faara, ƙǝs nda thlǝmadghǝn tǝ ndaarha, “A sǝnasǝ a ǝna ǝngya na heu ƙǝla kyaɗo ni a wumnda.”  
\v 6 Amma nanǝnya fǝrang nda tar firis Yeeso yanɗi na ngga kaan kalgha yi kaar, ƙǝla nana weerinda ɗǝfmiɗi ngga kaan, nanǝn Yeeso ni ishgha a pathlang Faara tǝ fiya. Ƙǝsǝr ǝnagha ndan aten weerinda ɗǝfmee na ngga.  
\v 7 Ƙǝsǝr andam mbǝ ˈyasǝ ɗimi aten ɗǝfmiɗi na kaar ya wa, kam mbǝm nggǝr kaɗa ɗǝfmee pak wa.  
\v 8 Amma Faara naɗǝ ɗimiyid nafiyighǝn ndǝn ndaanǝn, “Na sayi ɓayi, ndana Chinǝm, 
\q2 niya nggǝr fǝr weerinda ɗǝfmee tǝ nafiya Isǝreela hǝu tǝ nafiya Yahuda.  
\v 9 Mbǝ a naarha ƙǝla ɗǝfmiɗi ǝnani tǝ chichiyindan wa, 
\q2 a farɗi ƙǝs ni haar ndan kyang ni kanda sǝ hu chehweed Masar, 
\q1 ƙǝsǝr ish wanda aten ɗǝfmina wa, 
\q2 kang ƙǝsǝra ni kanda, Chinǝm ndagha kee. 
\q1  
\v 10 Kulo weerinda ɗǝfmina ni ya, niya ǝnarha tǝ nafiya Isǝreela, 
\q2 ndagha Chinǝm, 
\q1 niya chireethlǝng nggyahad na hai ahu huten nggindan 
\q2 tǝ hur yindan. 
\q1 Niya tsaurha Faar ndan 
\q2 kanda ƙǝm nafina. 
\q1  
\v 11 Mba nda nggǝr tsahang tula yindan ha, 
\q2 nduwa nggǝɗayi ndan tǝ ndaarha, ‘sǝnna Chinǝm.’ 
\q1 Ƙǝsǝr ko wunni nǝn a sǝn nggi, 
\q2 katǝrarha aten tǝfeewunda ɗǝgha hu tǝpamǝnda ɗǝ. 
\q1  
\v 12 Ƙǝsǝr niya chahang ɗimiyid ndan kanda ɗǝ, 
\q2 tǝƙǝm mbi nggǝr ɗal ɗimiyid ndan teena ɓalwa.” 
\p  
\v 13 Ndikna Faara aten weerinda ɗǝfmee, tsang ɗǝ yi katǝradghǝn suhurghǝn. Tǝƙǝm ˈya na yi ƙǝtǝm, tsauɗǝ suhur ɗǝ, tsǝɓaku nǝn a sahatta. 
\c 9  
\s1 Hurad ngyakhrha aten tǝrang shilee Faara in 
\p  
\v 1 Hu katǝra ɗǝfmee a pathlang Faara tǝ nafiya Isǝreela, na kwaman tǝrang shilee Faara in sǝ, tǝ mbǝd tǝrang shilee Faara in hu ƙǝshiirha.  
\v 2 Na ƙǝngya sǝ sǝri ahu cham Faarɗi. A hu yanɗi ƙǝnna na a mbee na mbǝd ɗǝfǝd patilla sǝ, tǝ tebǝr, tǝ mburodi ɗǝfang nanda ɗǝ. Yanɗi mbǝrha ya ndǝn na nda aarha mbǝrha na Chahal.  
\v 3 A pǝm shishamar ɗi ndǝghang nanda ƙǝnɗa sahai, na ƙǝnna sǝ yi sǝri na nda aarha mbǝrha na Chahal kaan.  
\v 4 A hur ƙǝnɗi na mbǝrha sǝ tangsang nanda tǝ tǝfasa ndǝna nda nji urdi sǝ na sǝdghǝn mbǝnggǝn a tenggǝn, tǝ akwati ɗǝfmee. Ənggini na sǝri ya ƙǝmang nda fadghǝn tǝ tǝfasa. Ahur akwatid ɗǝfmiɗi na tasau sǝ yi ǝna nanda tǝ tǝfasa na tǝ Manna ahurghǝn, tǝ sǝsal Haruna tǝfgha shee, tǝ mbǝd chireethla yi feera sǝri yi ɗǝfmiɗi.  
\v 5 Aten Akwatiɗi na ǝngya sǝ taksa na nda tǝ pakhkya fa na a kyad mamnggit Faara, kanda ni na fǝrang mishimnda mbǝɗi na nda aarha mbed tǝr hakked ɗimiyirha. Amma nanǝnya mbǝm mbang kala sǝ tǝtal tǝtal a tenggǝn wa.  
\v 6 A wumang nanda ǝnggina hai ya kiya, na firistaya ƙǝtsar narha kyarha hu ƙǝn yi tal ɗǝ, nanda narha ǝnna tar firis yindan sǝ.  
\v 7 Amma mamnda Firis katǝnggǝn ndǝna kyarha hu ƙǝn yi sǝri ɗǝ, nǝn kyarha mbǝɗaɗǝ saara tal hu hura kee. Mbǝ kyarha mbǝɗaɗǝ kula fara wa, nǝn ǝna sataka yi altenggǝn, tǝƙǝm fiya ǝnagha ɗimiyirha kula sǝndǝndan sǝ.  
\v 8 Hu kiya Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda a kyadɗǝ ndarha kwaman kyarha a mbǝɗaɗǝ na Chahal ingwaɗǝ a ɓal Chamɗa sǝ ƙǝt wa.  
\v 9 Yanɗiya ǝnsakhrha ni a ƙǝshiid weeriya. Nǝn a kyat ndarha ǝn fǝr yini tǝ satakhkini na nanda a fǝra mbǝ tsang hur nafini na a tǝrang shilee Faara in lǝlǝgɗa wa.  
\v 10 Tur ǝnggini ya nǝghǝn a ten hǝbrha tǝ sarha tǝ tsabya ɗǝɗamǝn-ɗǝɗamǝn. Tur ǝngginiya ngyakhkya ni kee a ten thlu farha na a ǝnagha fiya taara tǝghǝn kapa na weerindǝghǝn ɓarha ɓa. 
\s1 Far Yeeso ndana ka far sataka 
\p  
\v 11 Amma ɓad Ƙǝrǝsti ɓa ndǝn tsaunǝn ka mamnda Firis a ten ǝngya na nggǝngga nasǝ nanǝnya. Kyaɗǝ hur Chamɗa ɗǝ ǝnawana niifa tǝ haara, mbǝ tur yanɗi ǝna nanda ƙǝshiirha wa.  
\v 12 Kyaɗǝ mbǝɗaɗǝ na chahal kaan sara tal kee. Kyawa saɗǝ tǝ far ˈwalya nduwa yi wan thlaaya wa, amma tǝ yighǝn fara, walang nǝn ƙǝmsǝ hǝrǝkrha yi pakwanɗǝ.  
\v 13 Ngyakhrha Musa kyadɗǝ ndaarha nanda washang far ˈwalya tǝ far kwelya tǝ fish wan thlaaya a fiya fa ǝnagha ǝn tsanda. Yanɗiya ndǝna tsang fingya natǝ paarha fa tsawa nda chahal hu farha.  
\v 14 Nanǝn yanɗiya ƙǝkafǝk ni, ma nǝm ndaarha tǝ far Ƙǝrǝsti? Ndǝghǝn mbuwa tǝ ǝn ˈyaara fa, fǝrɗǝ altenggǝn a Faara hu Sǝsǝnɗi tǝ Peɗǝnda yi pa kwanɗǝ, ƙǝkafek na farɗi tsaɓang numad nǝm ɗǝ, hu ǝna ǝngya mbuwa ngga ƙǝsǝr ka ɗǝfang shilee nǝm Faara in na tǝ yibrha. 
\s1 Lǝghǝd ɗǝfmi ɗi hu mǝrra Yeeso 
\p  
\v 15 Tsaunǝn ƙee, Ƙǝrǝsti ndǝn ishgha hu weerinda ɗǝfmi ɗiya, ƙǝsǝr nafiya aah nanda na nda a thlǝ langaarha yi ɗǝfmiɗi pakwanɗǝ, ƙǝsǝr ˈwaɗǝ teena mǝrɗǝ shaulanggǝn fiya ahu ɗimiyid ndan ƙǝtǝm ahu katǝra ɗǝfmee. 
\p  
\v 16 A mal niifa ɗǝf miighǝn hai aten langadghǝn, ƙǝl a mǝr niifɗi a tsǝ laɓaara nda atenggǝn.  
\v 17 Ƙǝsǝr ɗǝfmee aten langaarha mbǝ ǝna taara wa ƙǝl a mǝr niifɗi, ƙǝsǝr mbǝ ǝna taara a ɓal niifɗi tǝ yibrha wa.  
\v 18 Ndǝn ǝnagha nden ɗǝfmiɗi yi ƙǝtǝm mbǝ tam ǝna taara wa ƙǝl tǝ irra fara ɗǝ.  
\v 19 Akwasamadɗi pǝrangna Musa ǝnɗi fiya na ahu ngyahadɗi, tǝranggǝn far wan thlaaya sǝ tǝ yi ˈwalya, wumanggǝn tǝ aama, nggǝrghǝn tǝrang wuhwar ɗǝfrha sǝ na nda aarha isob, tǝ was chaurarha na yiɓa tǝ farɗi washang nggǝnǝn ɗeleewar tsahadɗa fa tǝ fiya ƙǝm.  
\v 20 Tǝrgha ndǝghǝn, “Yanɗiya ndǝna farɗi tsaukwa yi ɗǝfmiɗi ndaana Faara a lafghǝn nun”.  
\v 21 Tǝƙǝm washang nggǝn farɗi aten chamɗi, tǝ aten kari heu na nanda manang thlǝm Faara tǝghǝn.  
\v 22 Ndagha ngyahad Musa kala ǝngya ƙǝl ana nda chahal tǝ fara, mbǝ chakh ɗimiyirha naarha sǝ a irr wa fara ɗǝ wa.  
\v 23 Tsauɗǝ tǝta ni ǝngginiya ana nda mǝmǝl, tsawa nda ǝn sakhkya na a talara na nda chahal. Amma ǝngya na a talara tafad ndan kamɗǝ a na nda chahal, tǝ satakhkya na ngga ma fingya yini ya.  
\v 24 Ƙǝsǝr Ƙǝrǝsti kyawa mbǝrha ɗǝ na chahal tǝnna niifa wa, ǝnsakhrha ni kee ƙǝla mbǝrha. Ɗǝghǝn talara ɗǝ tafadghǝn, ka ɗǝgha kyad fadghǝn a mbed Faara ƙǝsǝr ka ƙǝm.  
\v 25 Mbǝ ɗǝnǝn talara ɗǝ ka a nagha a fǝr altenggǝn atenggǝn-atenggǝn wa, ƙǝla na firis na manggǝn kyarha mbǝrha ɗǝ na chahal ka fad hurarha fa, tǝ fara mbuwa yighǝn.  
\v 26 A naɗǝ kee, ƙǝla tǝk Yeeso sǝsarha fa atenggǝn-atenggǝn, ka a katǝra ǝna ƙǝshiirha. Amma nanǝnya kyadɗǝ altenggǝn katǝra tal kee hu ngwala mii ƙǝshiirha ƙǝsǝr ka a tranggǝn sǝsǝmnda ɗimiyirha ɗǝ hu fǝr satakh fadghǝn.  
\v 27 Ƙǝla na niifa mǝra katǝra tal, akwasamadghǝn ƙǝl ngwa kumad Faara,  
\v 28 nǝghǝn kee ƙǝm fǝr Ƙǝrǝsti fadghǝn katǝra tal ƙǝsǝr ka a tǝranggǝn ɗimid fiya ɗǝ hangga. Ndǝghǝn nggi ƙǝm nǝn a nggǝr wutta ɓa yi sǝri, mbǝ ka a tǝranggǝn ɗimiyirha ɗǝ wa, amma ƙǝsǝr a hǝrghanggǝn fingya na ɓadghǝn ɓa a kukwasang kanda fa. 
\c 10  
\s1 Satakh Ƙǝrǝsti katǝra tal ni kee tǝƙǝm a heu 
\p  
\v 1 Ngyahad ɗeleewar Musa nǝghǝn ƙǝla mishimnda ǝngya ni na ngga ɓalgha ɓayi a mbee, mbǝ kad ǝnggina ni ya wa. Nanǝn kee tsǝkkwa kala fingya na a ndusang Faara fa tsawa nda lǝlǝgɗa aten satakhkini na nda fǝra ka fad hurarha fa wa.  
\v 2 A ndam na ngyahadɗi mbang, kam malang nda ǝna sataka. Hǝrǝmna nafiya na ɗǝfang shilee Faara teena ˈwanda teena tsau nda chahal, ɓalwa nda nggǝr numarha aten ɗimiyid ndan ɓalwa.  
\v 3 Amma aten turya satakhkini ya, na ɗal ɗimiyirha in sǝ ka fad hura fa,  
\v 4 ƙǝsǝr mbǝ tam ǝnarha hai far kwelya tǝ yi ˈwalya tsuthlang nda ɗimiyirha ɗǝ wa.  
\v 5 Tsaunǝn kee, sayidɗi ɓana Ƙǝrǝsti hu ƙǝshiirha ɓa, ndǝghǝn, “Satakhkya tǝ ǝn fǝrya mbǝ midwasǝ wa, amma farha ndǝna a ngweerha fa tǝghǝn.  
\v 6 Mba tǝk mbǝnda fa tǝ sataka yi njirha tǝ yi tsuwulth ɗimiyirha wa.  
\v 7 Tǝrgha ndee, ‘Kulo nggi ya, Faara, ɓani ɓa a ǝna ˈya ni na midwa, ƙǝla nanǝn chichireethlee hai aten na ahu ngyakhrha.’”\f + \fr 10:7 \ft Dzabura 40:6-8\f* 
\v 8 Katǝraghǝn ndaarha, “Satakhkya, tǝ ǝn fǝrya, tǝ satakhkya yi njirha, tǝ satakhkya yi tsuthlang nda ɗimiyirha ɗǝ, mbǝ midwa sǝ wa, mba tǝk mbǝndǝ ndan fa wa.” Ko nanǝn fǝrna ndan ƙǝsǝr ka ˈya ndana ngyakhrha.  
\v 9 Tǝrgha ndǝghǝn, “Kulo nggi ya Faara, ɓani ɓa a ǝna ǝnɗani na midwa.” Ɗǝfanggǝn katǝra ɗǝfmee a man patu ɗǝ ka a ǝna taara nda tǝ yi sǝri.  
\v 10 Ƙǝsǝr ka nggǝmnda Faara fa tsau ɗǝm chahal hu fǝrra satakh fad Yeeso Ƙǝrǝsti katǝra tal tǝ heu ƙǝm.  
\v 11 Kala parra fara kala firis nǝn isha aten targhǝn, nǝn fǝr tur sataka tal mbuwa tam tsaɓang ɗimiyirha ɗǝ.  
\v 12 Amma Ƙǝrǝsti fǝrɗǝ fadghǝn sataka katǝra tal yi kakwan, tǝrgha tsauka a yisǝmad Faara,  
\v 13 ka a farɗi nǝghǝn a ƙǝla fatsanggighǝn fa na a tsawa nda a kamughǝn.  
\v 14 Ƙǝsǝr ka fǝr sataka katǝra tal tsawang ɗǝ nafiya Faara a na nda chahal pakwanɗǝ.  
\v 15 Sǝsǝna tǝpeɗǝnda ƙǝm fǝrɗǝ shedawa, ƙǝsǝr ndǝghǝn,  
\v 16 “Yanɗiya ndǝna ɗǝfmiina niya ǝnarha tǝ kanda, a kwasamad sayidɗi, ndagha Chinǝm, niya ɗǝfang ngyahad na ahur ndan hai, tǝƙǝm chireethlǝng nggi hai ahu huten ndan.”  
\v 17 Tǝrgha ndǝghǝn, “Mbi ɗal ɗimiyid ndan teena tǝ aiben ndan ɓal wa.”  
\v 18 A chahang nda ɗimiyirha ɗǝ, ɓalwa satakh ɗimiyirha sǝ wa. 
\s1 Taama ɗǝm mbeeɗǝ tǝ naarha tsau tǝ Faara fa 
\p  
\v 19 Nanǝn kee, shayina, fǝrang far Yeeso kaali ƙǝm na a mbanggǝm ɗǝrha mbǝɗa ɗǝ na chahal.  
\v 20 Ndǝghǝn inangga kwamana ƙǝm hai, ndǝna kwaman yibrha, tǝ shishamar ɗi thlǝwusgha, ndǝna fadghǝn.  
\v 21 Nǝghǝm tǝ firis na manggǝn na a ǝna kutǝryirha hu wuri Faara,  
\v 22 Nanǝn kee taama ndusǝm a thlǝmad Faara ɗǝ tǝ hura tsahai, tǝ hǝhasyirha ɓagha ɓa hu fǝrƙǝkafek. Tama tsawum tǝ hura chahal, nagha hur nǝm tsahai kula ǝn ˈyaara a fad nǝm, tǝ kǝm fad tsab ɗaɗǝ tǝ aama na ngga.  
\v 23 Tama ƙǝs shiiten ɗa nǝm ha kula rǝbrha fa, fǝr nǝm shedawa tǝ shembe ƙǝsǝr niifɗi ɗǝfgha mee a ƙǝm nǝghǝn tǝ ƙǝkafek fa.  
\v 24 Tama kaɗa kwamana nǝm na a ɗanggǝm ndan sǝ hu nggǝmnda tǝ ǝna tarya na ngga.  
\v 25 A malang ɗǝm wumteena ƙǝla na fingya ǝnaarha wa. A meyedghǝn, taama fǝrang kaali nǝm ndan, ƙǝla sǝnnunsǝ takh far Chinǝm a nduwussa ɓa.  
\v 26 A ɗǝɗǝm mbeeɗǝ tǝ ǝna ɗimiyid thlǝmǝn a kwasamadɗi wal nǝm sǝnda yi ƙǝkafek, mbǝ fǝr sataka sǝ takhka na a tsaɓanggǝn ɗimiyid nǝm ɗǝ wa.  
\v 27 ˈYa takhka kee ƙǝl ƙǝla ngwa kumarha fa tǝ thlerra waarha na a njang nda fa sarya faara ɗǝ.  
\v 28 Kala niifa kargha ngyakhrha Musa fa na nda a ɓǝlang nda kula haɗang nda fa, aten ˈya thlǝkna shedawaya sǝri nduwa mahan.  
\v 29 Nafiya na a wal tsǝtsǝlla kaan ndǝna fingya kargha Wan Faara fa. Kanda ni nafiya ǝnagha ǝngya mbuwa chahal a far ɗǝfmiɗi tsawangga kanda chahal. Fingya ni ƙǝm sargha Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda ɓangga nggayid Faara ɓa. Sǝnggunsǝ nafiya kiya kamɗǝ nagha tsǝtsǝllǝ ndan pak ma fingya fiya wa?  
\v 30 Ƙǝsǝr sǝnɗǝm niifɗi ndagha, “Nggǝr haara mu yina ni, niya tiighǝn.” Nggǝrghǝn ndaarha, “Na Chinǝm a ngwang kumarha nafighǝn sǝ.”  
\v 31 Ən tǝrǝm nda ni na a kyagha niifa hu har Faara hai na tǝ yibrha ha.  
\v 32 Ɗalama teena hai tǝ tsawud ƙǝtǝm akwasamadɗi wal nun kukwaryid Faara. Ƙǝrǝs nun kaan hu yanda lǝghǝdgha tǝ sǝsaarha.  
\v 33 Fara sǝmǝn na fiya a ˈyar kun sǝsangganda kun a mbed fiya. Fara sǝmǝn ƙǝm na nda wumang kun tǝ nafiya na a sa tur sǝsadɗa fa ya.  
\v 34 Nuwun a sǝsaarha ƙǝla fingya na hu porsǝna, kun a kyad wutsǝfayirha akwasamadɗi thlang nanda karid nun, ƙǝsǝr sǝnɗun sǝ mbǝ ngaala sǝ wa nun a wal ƙǝnaghǝn na ngga yi pa kwanɗǝ.  
\v 35 Nanǝn kee a muwang ɗun hǝhasyidɗa ɗǝ kyanun ya wa, ƙǝsǝr na ƙǝnaghǝn sǝ kaan.  
\v 36 Kamɗǝ a ƙǝrsun nanǝnya, tǝnun ɗǝrha mbeeɗǝ tǝ ǝna ˈya na mid Faara. Nun a wal ǝnɗi ɗǝf nǝn miighǝn a kun.  
\v 37 Ƙǝsǝr “takhƙǝn ngguchit, ndǝghǝn ndagha nǝghǝn ɓayi nǝn a ɓarhaɓa mbǝ a tsǝrha titing wa.  
\v 38 Nafina na tǝ nggayirha fa na nda a tsaurha tǝ ƙǝkafek fa. Amma a wud niifa tal ahur ndan a samarha ɗǝ, mbi tǝk mbǝnda fa wa.”  
\v 39 Amma kǝm mbǝghǝm ahur nafini na wutta samarha ɗǝ sakhɗa nda wa, ƙǝm nǝghǝm ahur nafini fǝrgha ƙǝkafek walgha hǝrǝkrha. 
\c 11  
\s1 Kyad fǝrƙǝkafekirha 
\p  
\v 1 Nanǝnya fǝrƙǝkafek ˈyani nǝm shiteena atenggǝn, tsauka ˈya ni mbuwa nǝm mbang naarha tǝ yirha.  
\v 2 Hu fǝrƙǝkafek ni walna nafiya kaar faala a har Faara.  
\v 3 Hu fǝrƙǝkafek ni sǝnang nǝm hai tǝ ndaarha tǝ thlǝghǝd Faara ni ǝna nanda ƙǝshiirha, heu tǝ ǝngya nǝm naarha, kyagha nda ɓa hu ǝngya mbuwa nǝm a naarha. 
\s1 Hǝshya fǝrgha ƙǝkafek 
\p  
\v 4 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek ni fǝrna Habila sataka na ngga a Faara kalgha yi Kayinu. Hu fǝrƙǝkafekkidghǝn ni wal nǝn faala a har Faara tǝ ndaarha nǝghǝn tǝ nggayirha fa. Ko nanǝn Habila mǝrɗǝ, amma ƙǝsǝr ka fǝrƙǝkafekkidghǝn ɓalghǝn aten kaala sǝ.  
\v 5 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek ni tǝrang nanda Enok talara ɗǝ, ƙǝsǝr amawa nǝn mǝrra. Ndagha Ɗeleewar Faara, nawa ndan wa ƙǝsǝr tǝrang Faara ɗǝ. Kapa na nda tǝrang fǝr nda shedawa tǝ ndaarha ǝnaɗǝ ˈya mbǝnangga Faara.  
\v 6 A mbǝ tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek wa mbǝm tam ǝnaarha hai ǝna ˈya nǝm na a mbǝnanggǝn Faara wa. Ƙǝsǝr kaala niifa na ndusang Faara fa tǝtani a fǝrƙǝkafek nǝn tǝ ndaarha na Faara sǝ nǝn a fǝr ƙǝna taara a nafiya kaɗagha ndǝn.  
\v 7 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek Nuhu, a sayidɗi yiyang nanda thlǝmaarha fa aten ǝngya nawa na yirha, hu tǝrǝmnda yi na chahal taksa nggirggi aama nǝn ka a hǝrghanggǝn nafiyighǝn. Hu fǝrƙǝkafekkidghǝn ngwang ɗǝ kumarha ƙǝshiirha sǝ, tsauka tǝ har langaad nggayirha na kyarha ɓa hu fǝrƙǝkafek.  
\v 8 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek Ibrahim ǝnaɗǝ taara tǝ ˈya ndangna Faara a ɗǝgha mbǝrha ɗǝnǝn a thlǝ langadghǝn sǝ, kula ndǝghǝn sǝn mbǝɗi nǝn ɗǝrha saaɗǝ.  
\v 9 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek tsauɗǝ ƙǝla ronga hu chehwedɗi ɗǝfna Faara mighǝn nǝn a fǝranggǝn. Tsauka hu chamgya, ƙǝla ǝnana Ishaku tǝ Yakubu, kanda tsauka ƙǝm fa har langaad ɗǝf miiɗi.  
\v 10 Ƙǝsǝr Ibrahim nǝghǝn a ƙǝla wupǝri ɗa fa tǝnna Faara, wupǝri ɗi tǝnna Faara.  
\v 11 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek ni ko Saratu ni walɗǝ wee hǝshin, ko nanǝn kwarenga ni, ko nanǝn Ibrahim suhur ɗǝ kaan a sayidɗi. Fǝrɗǝ ƙǝkafek tǝ ndaarha na Faara a ƙǝs ɗǝf miighǝn.  
\v 12 Nanǝn ƙee, a fad niifa tal, suhurgha takhka a mǝra, ndǝn nggǝtgha turya hangga ƙǝla wufǝlngarya a fǝrakh amshi, tǝƙǝm ƙǝla wuchehweed kufaarha na a mii wuri aama mbuwa nǝm mbang thlǝɗang.  
\v 13 Nafini heu ya mǝrgha nda ɗǝ hu fǝrƙǝkafek. Thlǝwanda ǝnggini ɗǝfna Faara mighǝn wa, amma nagha nda ǝnggina ɗǝ ya inggun, tǝƙǝm nggǝmnda fa tǝ ndarha rongya kanda aten kwamana hu ƙǝshidɗi ya.  
\v 14 Nafini na ndaarha kiya, kyat nǝn ndaarha na nanda a ƙǝlarha mbeeɗǝ a wal chehweerha nda yi altendan.  
\v 15 Andam na nda a numarha aten chehwedɗi mal nanda a samarha, kama wal nda kwaman wutta ɗǝ.  
\v 16 Amma ɗǝf nda teena aten chehweerha na ngga kaan a talara. Ndǝghǝn ɗani shiɗang ngwa nǝn Faara a aaghǝn nda Faar ndan. Ƙǝkafek, tangsang ɗǝ wupǝri kanda sǝ.  
\v 17 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek ni Ibrahim a sayidɗi ƙǝƙǝrang nanda, fǝr nǝn Ishaku ka sataka. Wato, ndǝghǝn thlǝgha ɗǝf miiɗi nǝghǝn nggungwa fa a fǝr wanggǝn nǝn na tǝtal ƙee,  
\v 18 ko ndang na Faara, “A fad Ishaku ni na nda thlǝɗang nda tur yiwa.”  
\v 19 Ibrahim numaɗǝ tǝ ndaarha, Faara ndǝna mbang thleng mǝrya sǝ. Hu karapu, thleng ngganda Ishaku sǝ hu mǝrra.  
\v 20 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek fǝrang Ishaku parka Yakubu tǝ Isuwa aten ǝngya na ɓayi a mbee.  
\v 21 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek, Yakubu a sayidɗi nanǝn a mǝra, fǝrang ɗǝ parka wangya Yisufu kyab, tǝrang ɗǝ shilee Faara in a sayidɗi teheng nǝn fadghǝn aten sǝsalghǝn.  
\v 22 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek a sayidɗi takh na Yisufu a mǝra, ndik ɗǝ aten kyad wangya Isǝreelaya sǝ a chehweed Masar, tǝƙǝm malɗǝ pathla hai aten pangnda aal yighǝn.  
\v 23 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek ni a sayidɗi nggǝt nanda Musa ɓǝɓengga fa nggǝtyighǝn ndǝree mahan. Ənanda ƙee ƙǝsǝr sǝnda sǝ tǝ ndaarha wanɗiya nǝghǝn ngga, tǝƙǝm tǝrǝm ngwanda tǝ ˈya ndaana kutǝra wa.  
\v 24 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek sayidɗi manna Musa sǝ, kar ɗafa a aaghǝn nda wan wutarad Firˈauna.  
\v 25 Wurɗǝ a sǝsagha tǝ nafiya Faara ameyed tǝk mbǝnda fa hu ɗimiyarha yi ɓeena ngguchit.  
\v 26 Numaɗǝ a sǝsaagha ka Ƙǝrǝsti ma wal ƙǝna Masar nǝn, ƙǝsǝr njang ɗǝ yirha ˈya nǝn a waala a mbee.  
\v 27 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek ni malna Musa Masar, tǝrǝm ngwa sǝbrha hur kutǝra wa. Njiɗǝ teena ɗǝrha mbeeɗǝ ƙǝla nanǝn a njang yirha yanɗi mbuwana yirha a naarha.  
\v 28 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek ni laf na Musa wutsǝfayid tǝɗaarha ɗǝ, tǝƙǝm wash ɗǝ fara a mii kwad kirma ƙǝsǝr amawana tǝthlǝnda Faara ɓǝl fad wan ˈwaya tsuwar wan ˈwaya Isǝreelaya fa.  
\v 29 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek ni kyana Isǝrelaya ɗǝ tǝ wuri aama na yiɓa ƙǝla aten chehweerha na hwarghǝn. Amma na mid Masar yini ǝnaarha ƙǝla kanda hwaa nda ɗǝ.  
\v 30 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek ni chana kalthman Djariko hai, akwasamadɗi tiurang nanda hai yi ɓeena mǝd.  
\v 31 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek ni Rahab sǝsuwadɗi, ɓǝlang ngwanda hǝu tǝ nafini kargha mee fa wa, ƙǝsǝr thlǝɗǝ fa harmu chehwedɗi tǝ ɗǝɗemnggirha. 
\p  
\v 32 Ma ni nggǝr ndaarha? Mbǝ kwamana sǝ a harna na kalisǝ aten Nggidiyon, tǝ Mbarak, tǝ Samsǝn, tǝ Yefta, tǝ Ndauda, tǝ Samaila, tǝƙǝm annabiya wa.  
\v 33 Tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek ni thlang nanda kutǝryirha, ǝna nggayirha nda, wal nanda ǝngya ɗǝf nanda mighǝn tsauka ƙǝkafek, nggǝlang nanda mii lǝfariya.  
\v 34 Ɓǝlangganda sheneu waarha hai, hǝrgha nda ma chimnda thlaukh ƙǝlara. Tsangganda sǝsaukhkirha tsauka kanglang. Rǝk sodjaya chehweeya nda.  
\v 35 Fingya nishya thlǝnda mǝr yindan thleng nanda kanda sǝ hu mǝrra. Fingya ahur nafiniya sǝsang nda kanda, amma kanda ƙǝm kar nda fa a kal kanda nda hai, tǝna nda wal thliirha sǝ hu mǝrya hu tsaurha ɗǝ na ngga.  
\v 36 Fingya waa kanda nda, tsaɗa kanda nda, fingya ƙǝm ƙǝnang ngganda kanda tǝ wuyiwurra, muwangganda kanda hu porsǝna ɗǝ.  
\v 37 Fingya ɓǝlang ngganda tǝ mukrha tǝ ferya, fingya kudmangganda kanda hai sǝri, fingya ƙǝm ɓǝlangganda kanda tǝ thlaukh ƙǝlara. Na nda a wiirha hai tǝ pam chauraya tǝ pam ˈwalya a fad ndan. Tsawa nda hu yamirha, tǝ sǝsarha, tǝ ƙǝm kyala nda tǝ kanda.  
\v 38 Mbǝ ƙǝshidɗi ngga a kanda ya wa. Na nda a wiirha hai ƙǝla rongya a kaheerha tǝ wumngya. Na nda naarha mǝnda a kaɓeeya, tǝ kwaya na kamu chehweerha.  
\v 39 Nafini hǝu ya ko fal na Faara kanda aten fǝrƙǝkafekkid ndan, amma ko nanǝn ƙee, thlǝwanda ǝn ɗǝf miiɗi wa.  
\v 40 Ƙǝsǝr Faara ˈwaɗǝ teena fǝrang ɗǝ ˈya ƙǝm na ngga, nanǝn kee mba nda tam lǝghǝtta kula ƙǝm wa. 
\c 12  
\s1 Tsǝtsǝlyid Faara kyad nǝn nggǝmnda 
\p  
\v 1 Tsaunǝn kee, nanǝn muwang fa shedawa ƙǝm maɗufu, tama muwanggǝm kala ˈyaɗǝ na a ˈyaɗanggǝn ƙǝm fa. Taama muwanggǝm ɗimiyirha ɗǝ ƙǝsgha ƙǝm ha kenkeng, tama ƙǝm ƙǝrsǝm tǝ pǝpǝla ɗadɗi na a mbed nǝm.  
\v 2 Tama irang yirha nǝm Yeeso fa, ndǝghǝn na katǝra fǝrƙǝkafekid nǝm tǝƙǝm tǝ ɓangga lǝghǝtta fǝrƙǝkafekkid nǝm ɓa. Ƙǝsǝr ka wutsǝfayirha na a mbǝdghǝn, ƙǝrǝs ɗǝ kaɗidɗi, tsawang ɗǝ ǝn shilee ƙǝla mbǝ ˈyani wa, nanǝnya nǝghǝn tsau a yisǝmad tsǝnggam kutǝryid Faara.  
\v 3 Numama tǝ niifɗi ƙǝrǝsgha tǝ kaara ǝnangna fa ɗimiya fa, amawana mid nun ɗakhrha ɗǝ, nduwa malanggun shiiten nun. 
\p  
\v 4 A hu yan ndǝnun tǝ ɗimiyirha, tsǝkkwa na a irgha yinun fara ɗǝ wa.  
\v 5 Mbǝɗang nǝn kun tǝ laɓar fǝr kaali ndangna Faara kun ƙǝla na china ndang nda wanggighǝn wa? Ndanǝn, “Waana, kothlǝmaarha hai ana Chinǝm a taksorha, ma malang na sheng teena fa anaɗǝ a yanorha wa.  
\v 6 Ƙǝsǝr na Chinǝm tsǝtsǝl kala niifa nggǝm nǝn, tǝƙǝm nǝn tangsang kala niifa thlǝnǝn tsauka wanggǝn.”\f + \fr 12:6 \ft Karapu 3:11-12\f* 
\p  
\v 7 Ƙǝrsaama tǝ sǝsarha nun a tǝk fa, a tsauka tsǝtsǝlla ni na Faara a ǝnang nda kun ƙǝla wanggighǝn. Na wee sǝ mbuwa na chin tsǝtsǝlla wa?  
\v 8 A tsǝtsǝl wanda kun ƙǝla na wundakhnaya waala wa, wumiterya ni kun, mbǝ wangya hur minda ni kun wa.  
\v 9 Mbǝ ƙee ma wa, naɗǝm tur tsǝtsǝlla ǝnang na chingginǝm ƙǝm, fǝrang mamnggirha nǝm kanda atenggǝn. Ashe, mǝmǝlwa a nggǝmǝm fa tǝ tsǝtsǝlla Chinǝm yi Sǝsǝna, ƙǝsǝr ka a wal yibrha nǝm wa?  
\v 10 Chingginǝm yi thlu farha nanda tsǝtsǝl ƙǝm yi sayi ngguchit kee yi nggǝmnda hur ndan, hu numad ndan nǝghǝn ngga, amma Faara nǝn tsǝtsǝl ƙǝm ƙǝsǝr ka a ɗanggǝn ƙǝmsǝ, hu ǝnaarha kiya nǝm a tsaurha nafiya na chahal, ƙǝla ndǝghǝn.  
\v 11 Mbǝ tsǝtsǝlla sǝ nǝm tǝk mbǝndǝghǝn fa hu sayidɗi na nanda a ǝnaghǝn wa, nǝn hatta fa. Amma a kwasamadghǝn nǝn ɓang tsawud ɗǝɗemnggirha ɓa tǝ nggayirha a fingya walgha tsǝtsǝlla tǝghǝn.  
\v 12 Tsaunǝn ƙee pǝpǝnaman haryi nun ɗǝ tǝ waɗeeyi nun targha,  
\v 13 Pǝpǝnanggun kwamangya ɗǝ na ngga a saryi nun, ƙǝsǝr amawana sǝfǝngya wal tsǝrɓathla, a meyedghǝn wal ƙǝnda nda. 
\s1 Yiyi thlǝmarha aten kar nggayid Faara fa 
\p  
\v 14 Kaɗama tsawud ɗǝɗemnggirha tǝ kowunni, tsawama ƙǝm chahal, ƙǝsǝr mbǝ niifa sǝ na naa Chinǝm wa ƙǝl a naɗǝ chahal.  
\v 15 Kwarama naɗǝ niifa ƙǝɗeng nggayid Faara. Kwarama naɗǝ niifa tsaurha ndǝghǝn ni kul ndikrha sǝghǝn na ɓang nda sǝbrha ɓa, sǝɓanggǝn fiya ɗǝ hangga.  
\v 16 A sǝnunsǝ, a ǝna niifa kulafayirha, nduwa mbǝ tǝrǝm Faara wa ƙǝla Isuwa hengga mamnggidghǝn ɗǝ yi wan ˈwarha ka ɗeng ǝnnarhami tǝtali ƙee.  
\v 17 Akwasamadghǝn, ƙǝla sǝnnunsǝ, ana midghǝn sǝ a har langad parkad ɗa nǝn, kar ndan fa. Mbǝ ˈyasǝ nǝn mbang ǝnaarha na a nggǝranggǝn ǝnɗa hai ǝnan nǝn wa, ko nanǝn na midghǝn sǝ a wuɗanggǝn parkadɗa nǝn ɓa tǝ aam yirha.  
\v 18 Ɓawun ten wumnda Sǝnai ɓa nǝm mbang tsuwara fa wa, ko a thlǝmad waarha ɓa na ƙǝssa wa, ko a thlǝmad wula ɓa na tikɗik wa, nduwa kad ˈyaara,  
\v 19 nduwa pi kodwomnda, nduwa urarha na a ndikrha fa fingya na a sǝkkǝn a hwana nda tǝ ndarha a ɗǝnda mbeeɗǝ tǝ kalang nda kanda sǝ wa.  
\v 20 Ƙǝsǝr mbangwanda ƙǝrǝsta tǝ ˈya ndaana nda, “Ko maɓi ni tsuwargha wumndǝɗa fa, ƙǝl a muk kanda nda har mǝra nda.”  
\v 21 Ənɗi na nanda ya tsauɗǝ ǝn tǝrǝmnda ni kaan, ndǝn ndaana Musa, “Fadna a rǝbrha fa ƙǝsǝr ka hǝreenga.” 
\p  
\v 22 Amma ɓaɗun wumnda Urshalima ɓa, wupǝri Faara na tǝ yibrha fa, Urshalima yi talara, tǝ wumten wutsǝfayid fathlǝngya Faara mbuwa nǝm mbang thlǝɗang nda kanda.  
\v 23 Ɓaɗun thlǝmad fa takkwaya ɓa wan ˈwaya na thlǝmnggi ndan chichireethlee hai a talara. Ɓaɗun thlǝmad Faara ɓa na ngwang kumarha kowunni sǝ, tǝ thlǝmad sǝsǝngya nafiya Faara na tǝ nggayirha fa lǝlǝgɗa.  
\v 24 Ɓaɗun thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa, ndǝghǝn ishgha tǝ weerinda ɗǝfmee a pathlang Faara tǝ fiya, tǝƙǝm farɗi irang nanda ɗǝ na a ndikrha fa ngga kaan ma far Habila.  
\v 25 Kwarama, a karɗun yanɗa fa na a ndikrha fa wa. A sǝnunsǝ nafiya kargha sǝk Musa fa yiyangga thlǝmarha kanda fa hu ƙǝshidɗiya hǝrǝkkwa nda wa. Ƙǝƙǝn nǝm wal hǝrǝkrha a kar ɗǝm yanɗa fa na a yiyang thlǝmarha kǝm a talara hai?  
\v 26 A sayidɗi urad Faara tsang ɗǝ ˈya ƙǝshiirha fa. Amma nanǝnya ɗǝf ɗǝ mee tǝ ndaarha, “Niya nggǝr tsang ˈya ƙǝshiirha fa, mbǝ ƙǝshiirha katenggǝn kee wa, amma heu tǝ talara.”  
\v 27 Laɓarɗi ya, “Katǝra tal fadɗǝn,” kyadgha ndaarha na nda a ƙǝɗang ǝnɗa ɗǝ tsang nanda ˈya fa, wato nanda a ƙǝɗang ǝnggina ɗǝ ǝna nanda, tǝna ǝnggini mbuwa tsǝ ˈya fa tsaurha.  
\v 28 Tsaunǝn nǝm a thlǝ kutǝryirha mbuwa tsǝˈya fa, tama tsawum tǝ usarha, tǝrang shilee nǝm Faara in kamngga hu tǝrǝmnda tǝ fǝr mamnggirha,  
\v 29 ƙǝsǝr Faar nǝm ƙǝssa waarha ni. 
\c 13  
\s1 Satakhkya na mbǝnang Faara 
\p  
\v 1 Ɗama mbee ɗǝ tǝ nggǝm ndan yi wanmanggirha.  
\v 2 A malang ɗun ǝnang nggayirha nun rongya wa, ƙǝsǝr hu ǝna ˈya kiya ndǝn ǝnang na fingya taara fathlǝngya Faara, kula sǝndǝ ndan sǝ.  
\v 3 Ɗalama teena hai tǝ fingya ƙǝnang nanda kanda hai hu porsǝna, tsauka ƙǝla nuwun ƙǝƙǝna heu tǝ kanda. Tǝƙǝm fingya na nanda a sǝsang kanda, tsauka ƙǝla kunni na a sǝsarha tǝ kanda.  
\v 4 Kun heu a fǝrang mamnggirha nun kakhrha. Ngwa tsauka wusǝr kahad nun chahal, ƙǝsǝr na Faara ngwang kumarha nafiya sǝ na ǝna susuwayirha tǝ kulafayirha.  
\v 5 Nama inggun ma nggǝm wuɗǝɓǝla, usama tǝ ˈya nanun tǝghǝn ha. Ƙǝsǝr ndagha Faara, 
\pi1 “Mbi tam mal sa wa, 
\q1 Mbi tam kar sa fa wa.” 
\m  
\v 6 Nanǝn kee, taama nam hwas-hwas ndam, 
\q1 “Chinǝm tǝ thlarrǝ na ni, 
\q1 mbi tam tǝrǝm nda wa. 
\q2 Mana niifa tǝ wasa in ǝneerha?” 
\p  
\v 7 Ɗalama teena hai tǝ mamnggi nun pǝrangga Laɓar Faara kun. Ƙǝlaman tsawud ndan, tsahama tur tsawud fǝrƙǝkafekkid ndan.  
\v 8 Yeeso Ƙǝrǝsti ndǝghǝn ɗa na a ɓǝrarha, tǝ weeriya tǝ pakwanɗǝ.  
\v 9 Ma sakhɗang weerinda tsahaya huten nun wa. Kamɗǝ a wal kaali nǝm tǝ nggayid Faara, mbǝ tǝ ǝn tiina ɗǝɗamǝn-ɗǝɗamǝn yi hǝb ǝnnarhami mbuwa thlar nafiya na a takkwaghǝn.  
\v 10 Nǝghǝm tǝ mbǝd nji sataka mbuwana ko firistaya yi Cham Faara hǝbrha sǝ.  
\v 11 Na mamnda firis ɗǝrha tǝ far maɓiya a mbǝrha ɗǝ na chahal ka a fǝr sataka nǝn yi chakh ɗimiyirha, amma thlu maɓiyini nanda njang nda ɗǝ a ƙǝsǝr mbǝɗi.  
\v 12 Nǝghǝn ƙee ƙǝm sǝsagha Yeeso a ƙǝsǝr wupǝri ka a tsanggǝn fiya chahal tǝ farghǝn.  
\v 13 Nanǝn ƙee tama kyam sǝ ɗǝm thlǝmadghǝn ɗǝ, a ƙǝsǝr mbǝɗa ɗǝ, ƙǝrsǝm tǝ tur sara sanǝn fa.  
\v 14 Ƙǝsǝr ƙǝshidɗiya mbǝ wuri tsawud nǝm ni yi pakwanɗǝ wa; amma nǝm a kaɗa wupǝri na ɓayi.  
\v 15 Tsaunǝn kee, tama ɗǝm mbee ɗǝ fǝr sataka yi fal Faara hu Yeeso, ndǝna falla pǝr mamnggid thlǝmnggǝn.  
\v 16 Ma malang ɗun ǝna nggayirha tǝ wumteena tǝ ˈya nanun tǝghǝn ha wa, ƙǝsǝr tur satakhkini ya nǝn mbǝnang Faara.  
\v 17 Fǝraman mamnggirha mamnggi nun tǝƙǝm fǝra man aal tennun kanda, ƙǝsǝr na nda ƙǝla yiɓǝd nun ha ƙǝla nafiya na a fǝr kirǝssa tar ndan. A fǝrang ɗun mamnggirha kanda na nda a ǝna tar ndan tǝ wutsǝfayirha, a mbǝ kee wa, na nda a ǝnaghǝn tǝ sǝbrha hura, anaɗǝ kee mbǝ ˈyasǝ nǝn ɗang kun sǝ wa.  
\v 18 Hwanaman Faara kan teena. Sǝn fad nan sǝ na hur nan chahal, na mid nan sǝ a ǝna ˈya nan na ngga ƙǝtsar.  
\v 19 Niya hwan kun, a hwane Faara nun teena tǝni wutta thlǝman nun ɗǝ tsǝɓaku. 
\s1 Parka tǝ ngwala mii laɓara 
\p  
\v 20 Faara na fǝr ɗǝɗemnggirha ndǝn thlengga Yeeso Chinǝm sǝ hu mǝrra. Yeeso nanǝnya na tǝ lafrha na manggǝn ǝnana nda taara tǝ farghǝn ka a tangsanggǝn ɗǝf mii Faara yi pakwanɗǝ tǝ chiɓǝdghǝn.  
\v 21 Ngwa fǝrangga Faara ǝngya kun na nggǝngga ƙǝsǝr ka ǝnanun ǝngya na midghǝn, ngwa ǝna taara nǝn ahur nǝm mbǝnangga hu Yeeso Ƙǝrǝsti ndǝghǝn tsauna mamnggirha tǝghǝn pakwanɗǝ. A tsauka ƙee.  
\v 22 Niya hwan kun shayina, ƙǝrsaama tǝ yiyi thlǝmadɗi ya, ƙǝsǝr mbǝ laɓara ni nzang chireethlǝng ni kun ɗǝ wa.  
\v 23 Na minnasǝ a sǝnunsǝ tǝ ndaarha wanmanǝm Timoti kal ndan ɓa hu porsǝna. A ɓaɗa ɓa wet, nan a ɓarha ɓa kan kyab a ɓan na kun.  
\v 24 Ndaman ˈya mamnggi nun fa tǝ nafiya Faara na a mbǝɗi. Nafiya Faara na a Italiya kanda a ndang ˈya kun fa.  
\v 25 Nggayid Faara a tsauka tǝ kun hǝu.